title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-17-2014 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-17-2014 MON...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/17/14Monday, March 17, 2014 10:55 AM




Glenn and the guys are back and they've got some serious concern
          over Malaysian flight 370.  

They lay out their theories about what could have happened 
     and unveil the farce that is the media coverage over this event.

  Also, the story of a young boy being bullied because of his backpack
     and the ridiculous comments the school authorities made over this.

  Plus, the close comparisons between the U.S. and Mexico.
